  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/883780/extras/11c2885ffbf243403d3ea7b7794813be.avif?t=1601709400\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br>Wayblock is a New Puzzle Game! You can use just the available blocks (Wayblocks) to make a way until the Infinity fire. If you are Ready, click in the player and Go!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW WORLD!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/883780/extras/3ba272ec88fd43c789311b92ff2148df.avif?t=1601709400\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ICING ON THE CAKE</h2><br>The game will have constant FREE Updates. New stages, new worlds, new caracteres!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/883780/extras/83325d477bae4811a57a242fdcd2f3ed.avif?t=1601709400\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br><br>Welcome to the FREE Extra Content Bar! As soon as this bar reach 100%, the game will be updated with content of the next level TOTALLY FREE! Then, The Goal Update Bar will be go back to 0% and continue filling again. Share the game for your friends. The more the better!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/883780/extras/0637a533deb189227e85dc9dae1db908.webp?t=1601709400\" width=600 height=49 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> + 10 New Levels (Forgotten Green)</li></ul>Totalizing: 100 Levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/883780/extras/c0ca0bb9d75fba54003938f2ed12ac34.webp?t=1601709400\" width=600 height=49 /></span>",
